Douglas, Respondent, v. Banks, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 18, 1890.) Appeal from seventh district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Clapp & Mason, for appellant. Fettretch, Silkman & Scybel, for respondent.

Ho opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
